[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23469, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3684, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 354349, "username": "pygKent", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/pygKent", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02fb25370e33db233e7b6ee0b54d9a9c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02fb25370e33db233e7b6ee0b54d9a9c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02fb25370e33db233e7b6ee0b54d9a9c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1538937085, "last_modified": 1538937085, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "importmeta", "last_touched": 1780066926, "title": "干，好烦这种领导", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216381", "created": 1780022619, "deleted": 0, "content": "公司请了腾讯系的不干事大佬来当 CTO ，大力推动 AI （年龄 40+），说老板下了死命令要求全研发提效要达到 100%，因这个事，4 月份原本的普调，全公司其他部门照常调，就研发没有，说要等 Q2 季度结束，看看每个研发使用 AI 的情况再去调薪。\r\n\r\n每天开会时间多了两三个，大半时间都在开会开会开会，全是无效会议，单独给我们研发设立一个月度 OKR （其他部门照常季度 OKR ），还要求周末过来提升 AI 技能，当天要给日报\r\n\r\n关键是来了不作为，只会指挥，\r\n\r\n```text\r\n经常丢个链接， [新出了这个工具，去试试，看看能不能解决我们目前的问题，回头给我个报告] \r\n\r\n还时不时来一句 [吧你们的几月份到几月份的 ai 对话记录导出来给我] \r\n\r\n工期经常压， [这个需求太久了，用 AI 根本不用那么久（ 1 天的需求，要压成 2 个小时）] \r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n这是我随便挑的例子，离谱的话一堆，轻飘飘从他口里出来，完全不考虑下面的安排。我司之前不怎么加班，现在硬性要求加班到 8 点，产品需求做完没需求了，就自己给自己提技术需求，或者学习 AI\r\n\r\n还有，这人不以身作则，考勤也是随意的不行，经常早上不来，下午才来，每周五，下午 4 点就提前背包走了，来了差不多一年了，项目的营收一直在下跌，没有之前的好，一团乱，这人是老板花了半年软磨硬泡拉过来了，我是觉得一点用都没有", "content_rendered": "<p>公司请了腾讯系的不干事大佬来当 CTO ，大力推动 AI （年龄 40+），说老板下了死命令要求全研发提效要达到 100%，因这个事，4 月份原本的普调，全公司其他部门照常调，就研发没有，说要等 Q2 季度结束，看看每个研发使用 AI 的情况再去调薪。</p>\n<p>每天开会时间多了两三个，大半时间都在开会开会开会，全是无效会议，单独给我们研发设立一个月度 OKR （其他部门照常季度 OKR ），还要求周末过来提升 AI 技能，当天要给日报</p>\n<p>关键是来了不作为，只会指挥，</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-text\">经常丢个链接， [新出了这个工具，去试试，看看能不能解决我们目前的问题，回头给我个报告] \n\n还时不时来一句 [吧你们的几月份到几月份的 ai 对话记录导出来给我] \n\n工期经常压， [这个需求太久了，用 AI 根本不用那么久（ 1 天的需求，要压成 2 个小时）] \n\n</code></pre>\n<p>这是我随便挑的例子，离谱的话一堆，轻飘飘从他口里出来，完全不考虑下面的安排。我司之前不怎么加班，现在硬性要求加班到 8 点，产品需求做完没需求了，就自己给自己提技术需求，或者学习 AI</p>\n<p>还有，这人不以身作则，考勤也是随意的不行，经常早上不来，下午才来，每周五，下午 4 点就提前背包走了，来了差不多一年了，项目的营收一直在下跌，没有之前的好，一团乱，这人是老板花了半年软磨硬泡拉过来了，我是觉得一点用都没有</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780022619, "replies": 77, "id": 1216381}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 3241, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 2277, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 441627, "username": "mrsongopen1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/mrsongopen1", "website": "http://aimake.catmom.top", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e574/22f5/441627_mini.png?m=1779176626", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e574/22f5/441627_normal.png?m=1779176626", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e574/22f5/441627_large.png?m=1779176626", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e574/22f5/441627_xlarge.png?m=1779176626", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e574/22f5/441627_xxlarge.png?m=1779176626", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e574/22f5/441627_xxxlarge.png?m=1779176626", "created": 1568704052, "last_modified": 1779176626, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Rrrrrr", "last_touched": 1780071607, "title": "又快到续费车险的时候了，你们一年保费大概多少钱", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216382", "created": 1780022784, "deleted": 0, "content": "### 去年来了个五连撞，今天交强上浮了一百多。\r\n#### 讨论讨论，把你的保司，车型，投保内容和 保费分享一下\r\n#### 我先来：保司：太平洋、车型：21 款宋 plus 投保：300w+车损+交强 保费：3700", "content_rendered": "<h3>去年来了个五连撞，今天交强上浮了一百多。</h3>\n<h4>讨论讨论，把你的保司，车型，投保内容和 保费分享一下</h4>\n<h4>我先来：保司：太平洋、车型：21 款宋 plus 投保：300w+车损+交强 保费：3700</h4>\n", "last_modified": 1780025514, "replies": 67, "id": 1216382}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10938, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2337, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 673408, "username": "freefly111", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/freefly111", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e9727b8344edd5e420a47d5f8baebef9?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e9727b8344edd5e420a47d5f8baebef9?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e9727b8344edd5e420a47d5f8baebef9?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1706253543, "last_modified": 1779848145, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "MinonHeart", "last_touched": 1780105716, "title": "燃气灶 vs 电磁炉，到底哪个更省钱？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216454", "created": 1780036584, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近在纠结厨房主力灶具选燃气灶还是电磁炉，核心想问问大家：日常做饭，哪种烹饪方式长期更省钱？ \r\n\r\n有没有过来人给点真实经验～\r\n\r\n我个人更喜欢电磁炉，因为我不怎么炒菜，主要是蒸煮居多。用起来真的很方便。", "content_rendered": "<p>最近在纠结厨房主力灶具选燃气灶还是电磁炉，核心想问问大家：日常做饭，哪种烹饪方式长期更省钱？ </p>\n<p>有没有过来人给点真实经验～</p>\n<p>我个人更喜欢电磁炉，因为我不怎么炒菜，主要是蒸煮居多。用起来真的很方便。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780036584, "replies": 66, "id": 1216454}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 565, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 547, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 3285, "username": "cxd8190102", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cxd8190102", "website": "", "twitter": "ontos474238", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "深圳", "tagline": "", "bio": "AI 文档解析工具：https://knowhereto.ai/\r\nAI 自动填表工具：https://www.gosnapfill.cn/landing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_mini.png?m=1780045890", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_normal.png?m=1780045890", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_large.png?m=1780045890", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_xlarge.png?m=1780045890", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_xxlarge.png?m=1780045890", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_xxxlarge.png?m=1780045890", "created": 1290895441, "last_modified": 1780045890, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ludyleocn", "last_touched": 1780104438, "title": "Claude Opus 4.8 来了，但它说它是 qwen", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216494", "created": 1780041927, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天 Claude Opus 4.8 发布了，又一次升级，说现在已经支持在一次会话里调度几百个子 agent 同时干活了。\r\n\r\n虽然听起来又是一个新的 token 绞肉机，但是。。。利好一人公司！哈哈。\r\n\r\n但是我在评论区下面刷到了一个瓜，说 4.8 蒸馏了太多 qwen 等开源模型，导致自我认知出了问题，你现在问它是谁，它基本认为自己是千问，哈哈。\r\n\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/b3gfH8A\r\n\r\n不过它吹任它吹，别把 4.6 下了就行，我看他们说非编程感受还不如 4.6 ，不如等之后传说中更聪明的 Mythos 吧。", "content_rendered": "<p>今天 Claude Opus 4.8 发布了，又一次升级，说现在已经支持在一次会话里调度几百个子 agent 同时干活了。</p>\n<p>虽然听起来又是一个新的 token 绞肉机，但是。。。利好一人公司！哈哈。</p>\n<p>但是我在评论区下面刷到了一个瓜，说 4.8 蒸馏了太多 qwen 等开源模型，导致自我认知出了问题，你现在问它是谁，它基本认为自己是千问，哈哈。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/b3gfH8A\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://imgur.com/a/b3gfH8A</a></p>\n<p>不过它吹任它吹，别把 4.6 下了就行，我看他们说非编程感受还不如 4.6 ，不如等之后传说中更聪明的 Mythos 吧。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780042130, "replies": 54, "id": 1216494}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10938, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2337, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 588854, "username": "rivercherdeeeeee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/rivercherdeeeeee", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "13395218287", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4b10f242f87305c0a9ecc911f40d25a4?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4b10f242f87305c0a9ecc911f40d25a4?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4b10f242f87305c0a9ecc911f40d25a4?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1658461467, "last_modified": 1691203586, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "x4gz", "last_touched": 1780071924, "title": "家用落地扇推荐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216407", "created": 1780026051, "deleted": 0, "content": "家用落地扇推荐有什么推荐的吗，要求变频的，噪音小一些的", "content_rendered": "家用落地扇推荐有什么推荐的吗，要求变频的，噪音小一些的", "last_modified": 1780106777, "replies": 52, "id": 1216407}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630